high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the left knife on the counter.
Turn right, walk across the room and then turn right and step forward to face the white table.
Cut the tomato on the back of the table into slices.
Turn right and walk forward and turn left to face the first cabinet on the left.
Place the cabinet in the cabinet on the left.
Turn left and step forward and turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the slice of tomato on the white table.
Turn around and step forward to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and step forward to face the white table.
Place the tomato slice on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the table
Slice the tomato on the table
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go forward a bit, turn right in front of the cupboard
Put the knife in the leftmost cupboard
Turn left, go forward, turn right and go to the table
Pick up a tomato slice from the table
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the table
Put the tomato slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato and cook a slice of tomato

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the window, turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife closest to the loaf of bread.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn right and walk to the table.
Slice the tomato sitting on the back of the table next to the green sponge.
Turn completely around, walk to refrigerator, turn left and walk to the middle of the room.  Turn left so you are facing the waste basket.
Open the lower cabinet door next to the waste basket, put the knife inside, and close the cabinet door.
Turn left, walk to the wall, turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up a large slice from the center of the sliced tomato on the table.
Turn right, move forward a couple of steps, turn right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the tomato slice inside, close the door, turn on the microwave.  When the microwave turns off, open the door, remove the tomato slice, and close the door.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn right and walk to the table.
Place the tomato slice on the front of the table just below the horizontal spoon.
anns.task_desc: Warm up a slice of tomato and put it on the table.
